reviewText: Very nice if you're an EZ fan. It's like knitting with a friend. I love that it gives instructions on how to customize your knit and knit a smaller ribwarmer for children.

Have knit three Rib Warmers and love having this source to refer to for every part of the project.  I highly recommend this product if you intend on tackling any of these products.  Directions are clear and very understandable.
